column2: Some of the genomic variants, genes, nucleic acid sequences, or genomic regions on this list, and their use in specific applications, may be protected by patents.  Customers are advised to determine whether they are required to obtain licenses from the party that owns or controls such patents in order to use the product in Customer's specific application.  Unless expressly stated otherwise in writing by Illumina, Customer, and not Illumina, is solely responsible for obtaining such licenses.
